e":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d45acfe23a660e7a697269e7b8b031d8be0fc11","tid":2011434,"uid":42095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:09:47.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n統戰土共最拿手，好多人應該連點解都未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"因爲民主派陣營咁多年都無做過，淨係被統戰"},{"pid":"f1ed563cd7071f80a31204f423e9dd315c75626e","tid":2011434,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77275b5aa62dcf339e3178f9bd709e6c6863e0e3","tid":2011434,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:11:32.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n空投先係決定戰爭勝負的關鍵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我講緊歷史上戰爭最重要係空投補給物資</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家<span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好</span>空投任何會引致他人身體受嚴重傷害的物品</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n各位手足，任何行動<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不受傷不被捕</strong></span>真係最重要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大家有兩個重點一直做漏<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 小隊成員背景background check<br />\n唔好俾狗混入小隊裏面<br />\n2. 搵人做哨兵<br />\n及時發覺及避開危險</span></strong></span><br />\n[/member]"},{"pid":"4f7fe033103218745656ef97d88c55435bbcb3f9","tid":2011434,"uid":192754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply