升5-10%，可能會覺得無乜用但係呢個數唔係比你自己睇，而係整場運動同戰爭呢睇。<br />\n1萬人多1千人生存，100萬人多10萬人生存，已經係好大量人數，已經可以改變戰局。<br />\n唔係叫當手足係condoms ，每個人出事都好心痛，但係要適應痛苦悲傷，唔好打亂部署。<br />\n<br />\n如果，假如，退到去銀河系邊緣咁講。真係爆發第二次太平洋戰爭，黑警一定被迫入解放軍，如果大家唔走難加入盟軍，我地有準備先可以「極低限度」支援佢地，除非大家諗住外判戰爭比美國，咁就可以收皮。"},{"pid":"6c90b9d4df642599e21747b02abdb6331e380dab","tid":2011434,"uid":78892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a3978a03f4a96ff9ad0f51cad0356d43cd649db","tid":2011434,"uid":47084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:02:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7016d516fd38a590551a5982bacdf4a4b704e709","tid":2011434,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:02:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7a5e29df92f7792664ea532253864c6d31bd5a43","tid":2011434,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6371c15a92a2ad60bf19b02699e31f56295400c2","tid":2011434,"uid":286927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:55:30.000Z","msg":"Rui"}],"pinned":{"pid":"8b9b73b61b87d0e34b8dcc6c4a74622c65e6f97a","tid":2011434,"uid":221035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T04:36:14.000Z","msg":"推唔郁，重新開過"}}